    <subhead line="198">Tatiyakaṇḍa</subhead>
    <paragraph line="199" number="458">, 461<bold>Kvacādivaṇṇānamekassarānaṃ dvebhāvo</bold>.</paragraph>
    <paragraph line="200">Ādibhūtānaṃ vaṇṇānaṃ ekassarānaṃ kvaci dvebhāvo hoti.</paragraph>
    <paragraph line="201">Titikkhati <pageBreak edition="Myanmar" number="0.0234" />, jigucchati, tikicchati, vīmaṃsati, bubhukkhati, pivāsati, daddallati, dadāti, jahāti, caṅkamati.</paragraph>
