    <paragraph line="203" number="459">, 462<bold>Pubbo’bbhāso</bold>.</paragraph>
    <paragraph line="204">Dvebhūtassa dhātussa yo pubbo, so <bold>abbhāsa</bold>sañño hoti.</paragraph>
