    <paragraph line="216">Vīmaṃsati, tikicchati.</paragraph>
    <paragraph line="217"><bold>Vā</bold>ti kimatthaṃ? Cikicchati.</paragraph>
    <paragraph line="218" number="464">, 504<bold>Hassa jo</bold>.</paragraph>
