    <paragraph line="273"><bold>Hi</bold>vibhatti lopamāpajjate vā.</paragraph>
    <paragraph line="274">Gaccha, gacchāhi, gama, gamāhi, gamaya, gamayāhi.</paragraph>
    <paragraph line="275"><bold>Hī</bold>ti kimatthaṃ? Gacchati, gamayati.</paragraph>
