    <paragraph line="277"><bold>Hū</bold>iccetassa <pageBreak edition="Myanmar" number="0.0240" /> dhātussa saro <bold>e ha oha e</bold>ttamāpajja te bhavissantimhi, <bold>ssa</bold>ssa ca lopo hoti vā.</paragraph>
