    <paragraph line="296"><bold>Ghaṭā</bold>dīnaṃ dhātūnaṃ asaṃyogantānaṃ vuddhi hoti vā kārite.</paragraph>
    <paragraph line="297">Ghāṭeti, ghaṭeti, ghāṭayati, ghaṭayati, ghāṭāpeti, ghaṭāpeti, ghāṭāpayati, ghaṭāpayati, gāmeti, gameti, gāmayati, gamayati, gāmāpeti, gamāpeti. Gāmāpayati, gamāpayati.</paragraph>
